Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.48,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Akanecchi's up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:10.05,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Akanecchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.99,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.25,Main,Ogasawara,0000,0000,0000,,Go embarrass yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:31.63,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai said, "Be laughed at. \NBe laughed at, and become strong."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:36.52,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to \Nget laughed at, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.82,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Set...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.65,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,He got passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.62,Main,Kaneko,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:57.11,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you seen my potato \Nmascot around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:57.92,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.65,Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Potato? You mean that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.35,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.51,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.00,Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.62,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.06,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Is this yours, Mizuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.12,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.81,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I found it in the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.20,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.19,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I get so nervous without this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.95,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I even messed up today, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.82,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't like being \Nin front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:43.06,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's so embarrassing, \Nbut I really like running, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.86,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hopeless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.05,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.12,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:06.90,Main,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I think... you're fine the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.68,Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.01,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,The literature club has a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.79,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Pick out a book at random,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:31.34,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,and that book will give you the perfect \Nlife advice for your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:38.40,sign_13652_169_At_the_very_leas,Text,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I don't believe \Nromance comes down to chance.
