Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.26,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.69,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna train like mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:50.12,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:50.97,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow.
