Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.84,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, how was the meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.33,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I set a new personal best.
