Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.28,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.34,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My battery died...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:26.18,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my way home, \Nthinking you might be here...
