Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.18,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.77,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Keychains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.17,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Snacks for the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.25,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Curly-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.05,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.27,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.02,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind do boys like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.53,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:12.19,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I think the bigger one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.52,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.67,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We're choosing gifts for our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.69,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.95,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You know how guys eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.61,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.29,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.53,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. For reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.19,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:25.82,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.00,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.00,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Akanecchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.90,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.01,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You have someone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.59,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,If you're curious about \Nsomeone, that counts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:40.13,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone I'm curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.84,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Who? Who? Who? Who? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.02,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Hira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.46,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Did he ask you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.90,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Hira's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:53.66,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You should go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.44,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.29,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.99,Main,Shou,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.47,Main,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.74,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.75,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.57,sign_14160_153_What_s_up__,<-,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,1)}Azumi-kun: What're you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.64,Main,Tsubasa,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.56,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.93,Main,Setsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be the ones to get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.16,sign_17675_206_Hey__tomorrow__w,<-,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, tomorrow at 12:00 in front \Nof Doimaru Department Store
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.42,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Why so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.80,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.98,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:20.17,sign_17821_207_Huh__Say_what_,->,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.80,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.66,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.71,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,No secrets, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:32.92,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh... My parents are \Nasking about souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.98,sign_19430_229_Yasaka_Shrine,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasaka Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.54,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:42.54,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:43.86,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.40,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.07,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.51,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.78,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,We're torturing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.04,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.55,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Miu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.08,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:57.89,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.05,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.24,Main,Aira,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.32,sign_21821_255_I_m_at_Doimaru_D,->,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at Doimaru Department Store
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.57,sign_21821_255_Where,->,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.24,Main_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,He's not answering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.37,Main_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.78,Main_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I never even gave him an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.83,Main_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,He might not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.51,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:01.81,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.16,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.02,Main_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.90,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Azumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.45,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.43,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Some stuff happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.39,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.57,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.34,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.65,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.37,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.53,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to meet you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.85,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,so I came, but you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.19,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining, and you aren't \Nanswering your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.16,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:23.12,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher took my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.05,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why Chinatsu's phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.70,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.28,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,She just happened to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:33.88,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:36.75,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.94,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.25,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:46.24,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but we can't \Neven talk at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.41,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.52,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:57.76,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,to talk with you more, Azumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.22,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.59,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.47,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.99,sign_8674_66_Things_you_shoul,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Things you shouldn't do\N in a relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.99,sign_8674_67_1__Don_t_text_or,Text,0000,0000,0000,,1. Don't text or LINE too much\N{\c&H747184&\fs16}— Boys hate needy girls\N{\c&H9D7DBC&\fs18}2. Think about how often you reply\N{\c&H747184&\fs16}— Don't reply right away, \Nbut don't wait too long, either
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.05,sign_8674_67_1__Don_t_text_or,Text,0000,0000,0000,,3. Don't text or LINE during a date\N{\c&H747184&\fs16}— Do you have a habit of reacting\Nas soon as you get a message \Nfrom your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.39,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Dating is so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.94,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go to that cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.27,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.45,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your LINE ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.10,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:46.87,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.28,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.57,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.47,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.10,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.52,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the place okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.57,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I used Maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.59,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,How did the exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.17,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.57,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.40,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I did awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.61,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.05,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.88,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Your novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:25.71,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.32,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.15,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.05,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.73,sign_30168_304_Chinatsu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.36,sign_30204_306_Notice_to_Akane_,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Notice to Akane!\NI think I have a crush on Azumi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.73,sign_30240_307_I_think_I_have_a,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a crush on Azumi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.16,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:17.56,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.11,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.37,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,What flavor is yours, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.53,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kinako mochi soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.13,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let me taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.34,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:36.09,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the publisher called me and \Nsaid they wanted to meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.71,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.19,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.08,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.63,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what they want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.61,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You might be winning that award.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.47,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.84,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:48.91,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.42,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.36,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream might come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:57.36,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.78,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.43,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The same day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.02,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't come cheer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.38,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.20,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The same day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.00,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.16,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.70,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:28.83,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.02,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:34.18,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.72,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.41,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.40,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.35,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.96,sign_12764_114_Azumi_kun,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Azumi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.96,sign_12764_115_Here_goes,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.29,sign_12902_116_Here_goes,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.29,sign_12902_117_Pinky_promise,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Pinky promise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.93,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.47,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.30,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.68,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,About that LINE message the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.77,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.51,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.48,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.16,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,in... a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:33.42,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,W-With Azumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.55,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:40.96,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.28,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.34,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.08,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:55.90,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.35,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno, slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.06,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,We're searching for young writers right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.79,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.76,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You're in middle school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.53,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.78,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, being so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.44,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, I don't think you're \Ncut out for serious literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:33.30,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try \Nlight novel-type stuff instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.91,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling you could do it, Azumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.16,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.75,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,What happened today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.93,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't focused at all, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.43,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you could make it to prefecturals.
